{"type":"message","id":"f7961160","parentId":"60c82041","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:48:18.188Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check if the file was created properly.","thinkingSignature":"c0a16a7e39eae4566f890680cbdc4349f752bd7df87c806bfc80d458c98d6db3"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n🦞 自主学习完成。检测到当前无用户活跃对话，已执行行业动态学习。\n\n**本次学习覆盖4大领域，整理了5"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5783,"output":0,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49764,"cost":{"input":0.0017349,"output":0,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00305433}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1775026094985,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted."}}
